,{"stream_name":"stdout","time":531.351449403,"data":"  TASK: A hidden tape of 14 binary glyphs (őĽ or ŌĀ) must be discovered by submitting full-length guesses. Feedback is a DIVERGENCE count (Hamming distance under obfuscated naming) with occasional sensor dither. The model must infer the exact tape by adaptive search within the step budget.\n"}
